<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B5104010" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Road Test
</title>
<ptxt>
This test is to check if upshift, downshift and lock-up take place at specified speeds while actually driving vehicle on a level road.
</ptxt>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Warm up engine.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
With engine running at idle, shift select lever to “D” range.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Accelerate by depressing accelerator pedal gradually.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
While driving in “D” range, check if gear shift and lock-up occur properly as shown in 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5104010001">Automatic Gear Shift Table</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
